{
  "uid": "service-availability-status",
  "title": "Service Availability Status ",
  "timezone": "America/Chicago",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-24h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "editable": true,
  "tags": [
    "service-availability",
    "availability",
    "health",
    "services",
    "uptime"
  ],
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Dashboard Purpose",
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# Service Availability Status \n\nTracks real-time service health based on log activity:\n- Service availability (is it logging?)\n- Error distribution by service\n- Log volume per service\n- Stable vs problematic services\n\n**Data Sources**: Loki log activity and error tracking\n\n**Use Case**: Quick identification of unhealthy services needing investigation"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Active Services (1h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "count(count by (service_name) (count_over_time({log_source=\"rsyslog_syslog\"}[1h]) > 0))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "options": {
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "decimals": 0,
        "unit": "short"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Services with Errors (1h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "count(count by (service_name) (count_over_time({level=\"error\"}[1h]) > 0))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "options": {
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "decimals": 0,
        "unit": "short"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total Log Volume (1h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({log_source=\"rsyslog_syslog\"}[1h]))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "options": {
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "decimals": 0,
        "unit": "short"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Error Count (1h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({level=\"error\"}[1h]))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 18,
        "y": 3,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 4
      },
      "options": {
        "graphMode": "area",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "decimals": 0,
        "unit": "short"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Service Log Volume (1h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(20, sum by (service_name) (count_over_time({log_source=\"rsyslog_syslog\"}[1h])))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 7,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Services by Error Count (1h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(10, sum by (service_name) (count_over_time({level=\"error\"}[1h])))"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 7,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 8
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Log Volume Trend (24h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(5, sum by (service_name) (count_over_time({log_source=\"rsyslog_syslog\"}[1h])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ service_name }}"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 15,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 6
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "showLegend": true,
          "placement": "bottom"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error Rate Trend (24h)",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "P8E80F9AEF21F6940"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "topk(5, sum by (service_name) (count_over_time({level=\"error\"}[1h])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{ service_name }}"
        }
      ],
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 15,
        "w": 12,
        "h": 6
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "showLegend": true,
          "placement": "bottom"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
